! Cascade Palette

;Hotkey
:The palette opens with the shortcut configured at <code>$:/config/shortcuts/rimir-cascade-palette-open</code>. Default: ''Ctrl-Space''. Edit that tiddler to rebind.

;Behaviour
:* ''Max results per stage'' — caps the number of items rendered per stage. Default 30. Configured at <code>$:/config/rimir/cascade-palette/max-results</code>.
:* ''Soft depth warning'' — engine logs a warning to the console if stack depth exceeds this. Default 10. Configured at <code>$:/config/rimir/cascade-palette/soft-depth-warning</code>. No hard cap.
:* ''Show perf footer'' — toggle a small diagnostic footer with recompute / render timings and item counts. Off by default. Configured at <code>$:/config/rimir/cascade-palette/show-perf-footer</code>.

;Diagnostics
:* See all loaded entries: <$button>List entries<$action-navigate $to="$:/temp/cascade-palette/entries-listing"/></$button>
:* See all loaded actions: list any tiddler tagged ''`$:/tags/rimir/cascade-palette/action`''.
